snippet.title: Real VR Fishing - Official US East DLC Teaser Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Real VR Fishing is a VR fishing game where players can go fishing, catch various species, and fill their aquariums. The US East DLC is releasing for Real VR Fishing that allows players to fish near the Statue of Liberty, off the coast of the Freedom Tower, and more. The US East DLC for Real VR Fishing is releasing soon for Meta Quest.

#GameTrailers #VR #SummerofGaming
